Class LowerBoundConstraint<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • constraints.LowerBoundConstraint<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type for which the lower bound is defined

    ArgumentConstraint<T> 

    public class LowerBoundConstraint<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ArgumentConstraint<T>
    This class represent a constraint which is fulfilled when the argument value is higher or equal than the specified lower bound
